text.tspan: Excess mortality: Raw number of deaths from all causes
compared to projection based on previous years, United
The reported number of weekly or monthly deaths in 2020–2023 and the projected number of deaths for 2020, which
is based on the reported deaths in 2015–2019. The reported number might not count all deaths that occurred due to
incomplete coverage and delays in reporting.
Data source: Human Mortality Database (2023), World Mortality Dataset (2023)
